                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">F. 5a: Note in Amharic, "It is 1476 years since monasticism 
                        
                        began. " </item><item xml:id="a2"><desc type="GuestText">Ff. 28b-29b: Long prayer in Amharic for God’s indulgence and 
                        
                        forgiveness and preservation from death.</desc></item> 
                        
                        <item xml:id="e1">Copied for Gabra Mika’el (prayers, ff. 12b, 13a, l 6 a, 27b and 30a). Other 
                        names have also been inserted in prayers, namely, Walda Yohannes (f. 13b ), 
                        Habta Maryam (f. l4a), and Gabra Heywat (f. 17a). </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="e2">Stamp of the Patriarchate Library, ff. la, 3a, 17a, 30a, 37a, 40a, 53b 
                        and 63 b. </item>
                        
                       <item xml:id="e3"> Contents of the manuscript, f. la.</item> 
